      <title>印度石油公司正在与国家核公司就小型反应堆进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/indian-oil-in-talks-with-state-nuclear-firm-for-small-reactors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国营印度石油公司正在与印度原子能垄断公司就建造小型核电站进行初步谈判，这项早期技术被视为大型核电站的经济高效替代方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/indian-oil-in-talks-with-state-nuclear-firm-for-small-reactors</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:50:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
