      <title>Blue Owl 将在最新保险交易中收购 Kuvare Asset Management</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/blue-owl-to-buy-kuvare-asset-management-in-latest-insurance-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Blue Owl Capital Inc. 已同意收购 Kuvare Asset Management，这一最新交易凸显了私募市场投资公司在保险市场上开发资产池的努力。]]></description>
