      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国放宽汽车贷款规则以刺激消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/china-moves-to-boost-ev-sector-by-relaxing-auto-loan-ratios</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国希望通过其庞大的汽车行业提振疲软的消费者信心，中国放宽了购买私家车的贷款难度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/china-moves-to-boost-ev-sector-by-relaxing-auto-loan-ratios</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 08:26:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德和 KKR 将阿布扎比国家石油公司石油管道股份出售给阿布扎比</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/blackrock-kkr-sell-adnoc-oil-pipeline-stake-to-abu-dhabi-firm-lujixlxn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BlackRock Inc. 和 KKR &amp;收购阿布扎比石油管道网络 40% 的股份五年后，该公司将其出售给一家总部位于阿布扎比的公司，该交易标志着外国资产管理公司对海湾国有能源公司基础设施的首次投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/blackrock-kkr-sell-adnoc-oil-pipeline-stake-to-abu-dhabi-firm-lujixlxn</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 08:06:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在鲍威尔发表讲话之前，黄金价格从新纪录回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/gold-hits-record-as-silver-surges-on-outlook-for-fed-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名美联储官员表示，他们仍预计美联储今年将降息三次，主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔将于周三晚些时候发表讲话，金价从新纪录回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/gold-hits-record-as-silver-surges-on-outlook-for-fed-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 01:53:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
